      "paragraph_name": "2000-READ-ROOT-SEG-FILE",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph reads a record from INFILE1. If the read is successful (WS-INFIL1-STATUS is spaces or '00'), the record is moved to PENDING-AUTH-SUMMARY, and 2100-INSERT-ROOT-SEG is performed to insert the root segment into the IMS database. If the read is unsuccessful and the file status is '10' (end-of-file), END-ROOT-SEG-FILE is set to 'Y'. If the read is unsuccessful and the file status is not '10', an error message is displayed. This paragraph manages the reading of root segment records and delegates the insertion process to another paragraph.",
